<lb n="4" break="no"/>tputrīva caṇḍīpatēḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> dēvī boppamapūrvvikārtthijanatākalpapratānī<unclear>svayaṁ</unclear> dhairyyaudāryyasuvīryyakāryyavilasat cātu<unclear>ryya</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dhuryya śriyyaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] śākābdē bāṇanāgāṁbaraśaśigaṇitē kṛṣṇapakṣē vidhātustithyāṁ mārttaṇḍavārē dinakṛti viṣuvē prasthitē <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>rāśiṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dīpaṁ prādādakhaṇḍaṁ tribhuvanapatayē bhīmanādhāya bhaktyā boppādēvī śivārccōrjjitama<unclear>ti</unclear>vibhavā duggabhūpā<unclear>la</unclear>
