<lb n="8" break="no"/>ggalakṣmiyaina boppādēvulu śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvarakuṁ beṭṭina Akhaṇḍavarttilōhada <unclear>ṇḍu</unclear> di1 ṇṭiki kilaramuna bōlu na<unclear>lvu</unclear>
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ruṁ buṇṭagā modali Aḍapuna tallanapōmana vasamunaṁ beṭṭina InupaEḍlu 50 ṇṭiki Ācaṁdrārkkamu nityapaḍi gola <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
